Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.82,0:00:12.08,Matsumoto,Matsumoto,0,0,0,,I wonder if this guy is gonna be alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.08,0:00:12.88,Tanaka,Tanaka,0,0,0,,It's 24 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.90,0:00:14.93,Matsumoto,Matsumoto,0,0,10,,The first time I saw him I thought
