Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.61,0:00:20.62,Matsumoto,,0,0,10,,He jumped right out of volume 8.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.00,0:00:29.77,Title 1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\pos(701.887,834.693)\3c&HFFFFFF&\3a&H32&}24 Hour {\4c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4a&HFF&\c&H000000&}Long Interview
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.42,0:00:25.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,So far, both Tsukitei Hosei and Drunk Dragon's Suzuki Taku
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.25,0:00:27.84,Narrator,,0,0,0,,have challenged the 24 hour long interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.84,0:00:29.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{\c&HDEC71B&}I've broken a lot of people's bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.93,0:00:38.48,Title 2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\3c&HFFFFFF&\3a&HC8&\c&HFFFFFF&\pos(724.528,868.995)}Talk about their life nonstop for {\c&H00FFFB&\4c&H000000&\4a&HFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\3a&HC8&}24 hours
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.26,0:00:32.66,Narrator,,0,0,0,,During this segment, one has to talk nonstop
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.67,0:00:36.33,Narrator,,0,0,0,,about their own life so far for 24 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.33,0:00:38.48,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The one who will challenge it this time is...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.92,0:00:42.52,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Tonight's special guest is Jimmy Onishi, welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.29,0:00:50.18,Title 3,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\pos(703.396,909.218)}Jimmy Onishi (52)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.82,0:00:49.10,Yamazaki,,0,0,10,,You just pulled the red curtain right over you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.10,0:00:51.89,Matsumoto,,0,0,10,,You've probably been hiding back there since yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.69,0:00:56.02,Matsumoto,,0,0,10,,Recently you've been in all kinds of TV shows.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.02,0:00:57.88,Narrator,,0,0,10,,Well, since you let me show up here every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.88,0:00:59.88,Matsumoto,,0,0,10,,Yeah, at the No Laughing Series.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.88,0:01:01.45,Narrator,,0,0,10,,That has really helped me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.45,0:01:03.76,Matsumoto,,0,0,10,,But you've shown up at all these popular shows
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.76,0:01:04.94,Matsumoto,,0,0,10,,that suddenly wanted you as a guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.94,0:01:07.26,Yamazaki,,0,0,10,,Shows like Golden and Gan Gan, right Jimmy?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.34,0:01:10.09,Matsumoto,,0,0,10,,Have any of those appearances left you anything good?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.22,0:01:13.85,Narrator,,0,0,10,,Well, {\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}maybe {\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H000000&}1 good hit out of 10 swings.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.85,0:01:15.85,Hamada,,0,0,0,,It's not that many...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.45,0:01:16.85,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,It's only 10 percent.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.69,0:01:19.85,Yamazaki,,0,0,0,,I think that's too many swings.
