Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.24,0:02:33.98,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\pos(1215.094,993.687)}Return to TV
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.28,0:02:29.09,Narrator,,0,0,10,,During this interview we will be using this time-line
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.09,0:02:33.52,Narrator,,0,0,10,,to go over everything that has happened in Jimmy's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.16,0:02:38.37,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Today I'd like to start our 24 hour interview with your birth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.05,0:02:38.53,Jimmy,,0,0,0,,Sure
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.53,0:02:40.72,Staff,,0,0,10,,Jimmy, when were you born?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.92,0:02:44.28,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,I was born on January 1st, 1964.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.01,0:02:45.49,Endo,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1151.698,911.229)}On New Year's Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.29,0:02:46.28,Staff,,0,0,10,,You were born on New Year's Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.28,0:02:48.28,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.74,0:02:52.98,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The interview starts with some personal questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.34,0:02:55.41,Staff,,0,0,10,,What's your real name?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.41,0:02:57.00,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,Um, Onishi Hideaki
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.12,0:02:58.81,Staff,,0,0,10,,So your name is Hideaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.94,0:03:01.41,Staff,,0,0,10,,Can you explain the meaning behind your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.61,0:03:03.97,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,Onishi...um...the Onishi...well,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.97,0:03:06.18,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,there's nothing I could do about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.18,0:03:08.18,Matsumoto,,0,0,10,,You don't need to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.76,0:03:10.86,Yamazaki,,0,0,10,,You couldn't do anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.92,0:03:14.12,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,The "Hide"came from Toyotomi Hideyoshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.12,0:03:19.28,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,because he was born on January 1st.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.72,0:03:23.88,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,And then the "Ake" came from the phrase for "Happy New Year".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.10,0:03:28.00,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,That's the meaning behind "Hideaki".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.10,0:03:26.04,Endo,,0,0,10,,{\pos(1181.887,718.045)}So there was a meaning \Nbehind the name.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.33,0:03:31.06,Staff,,0,0,10,,How many people were there in your family?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.16,0:03:32.74,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,My family was...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.74,0:03:36.98,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,My dad, my mom...um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.98,0:03:37.60,Hamada,,0,0,10,,Say it quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.60,0:03:39.60,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,My older brother and me for a total of four.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.60,0:03:39.60,Matsumoto,,0,0,10,,{\pos(236.981,927.207)}Wow, that's scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.57,0:03:42.81,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,Jimmy was raised in a family of four.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.68,0:03:43.84,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,{\pos(418.113,875.028)}Why didn't you remember your brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.85,0:03:45.25,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,But what were his parent's {\3c&H000000&\c&H00FFEE&}personalities{\c&HFFFFFF&} like?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.40,0:03:49.58,Staff,,0,0,10,,I'd like to know what kind of people were your parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.76,0:03:51.89,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,My dad was...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.24,0:03:56.90,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,an alcoholic... so he drank all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.90,0:03:59.92,Staff,,0,0,10,,What kind of father was he at home? Was he scary?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.92,0:04:02.14,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,He had a lover so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.14,0:04:05.60,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,He didn't spend much time at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.68,0:04:10.90,Staff,,0,0,10,,{\fad(250,250)}{\pos(994.717,1076.034)}When did you learn he had a lover?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.00,0:04:15.20,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,Some time before my dad retired...my mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.20,0:04:21.76,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,found a letter from his lover inside his suit's inner pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.76,0:04:25.73,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,When she opened and read it, it said... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.36,0:04:37.04,Staff,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)\pos(638.491,852.905)}{\i1\4c&HFFFFFF&\4a&HFF&\pos(721.51,854.916)}I've been by your side for{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.28,0:04:37.04,Staff,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)\pos(976.604,852.905)}{\i1\4c&HFFFFFF&\4a&HFF&\pos(721.51,854.916)}35 years,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.09,0:04:33.80,Staff,,0,0,10,,That long?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.13,0:04:33.77,Jimmy,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.77,0:04:37.04,Staff,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)}{\pos(718.491,915.084)}{\i1\4c&HFFFFFF&\4a&HFA&}thank you for making me so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.04,0:04:39.94,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,{\pos(991.698,1076.034)}I thought he did a really good job hiding it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.60,0:04:43.56,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,{\pos(774.34,1061.955)}Next, an episode about his {\c&H00FFEE&\3c&H000000&}mother{\c&HFFFFFF&}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.56,0:04:46.01,Staff,,0,0,0,,What kind of parent was your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.22,0:04:49.73,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,She used to work at the cafeteria of what is now NTT.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.74,0:04:53.48,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,"You won't be able to speak on the same level as your parents
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.48,0:04:58.74,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,until you start bringing your own money to the house."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.17,0:05:01.37,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,She used to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.37,0:05:04.78,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,That's why I started delivering newspapers since the 4th grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.78,0:05:06.38,Staff,,0,0,10,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.64,0:05:06.28,Jimmy,,0,0,0,,{\pos(713.962,945.419)}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.38,0:05:11.08,Jimmy,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1053.585,651.788)}I was a young worker.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.72,0:05:10.64,Staff,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.16,0:05:15.36,Staff,,0,0,10,,I'd like to learn about the influence your parents gave you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.42,0:05:19.02,Staff,,0,0,10,,First, what kind of influence did you get from your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.02,0:05:21.81,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,My dad taught me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.81,0:05:25.34,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,"Imagine everyone around you is a thief."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.34,0:05:27.41,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,My mom taught me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.50,0:05:30.42,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,"Don't touch other people's belongings."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.42,0:05:34.05,Matsumoto,,0,0,10,,Something like the {\c&H000000&}shield and the spear.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.92,0:05:34.54,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,{\pos(217.359,901.173)}Opposite... \Nthey're opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.16,0:05:35.04,Endo,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1207.548,885.084)}Complete opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.12,0:05:41.34,Narrator,,0,0,10,,Growing up in that family, what kind of child was Jimmy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.50,0:05:44.10,Staff,,0,0,0,,I'd also like to ask about kindergarten.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.10,0:05:46.61,Staff,,0,0,10,,Do you remember anything about kindergarten?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.70,0:05:49.24,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,According to things I've heard from others...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.24,0:05:52.34,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,I was always alone... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.45,0:05:56.41,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,playing with wooden blocks or pretending I was a train.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.41,0:06:01.14,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,I guess I didn't mix too well with everyone else... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.14,0:06:03.62,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,I wasn't able to speak at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.62,0:06:06.32,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,My mom said "I'll take him to the hospital."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.32,0:06:09.20,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,My grandmother said "It won't do any good if you take him."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.20,0:06:12.76,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,"He'll learn to speak eventually." And well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.92,0:06:18.06,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,In elementary school there was a girl I really liked.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.06,0:06:22.70,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,So the first word I spoke was "like".
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.70,0:06:26.24,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,I liked a girl called Maki.
