Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.30,0:07:53.30,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,That's the only thing I can remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.30,0:07:53.30,Matsumoto,,0,0,10,,{\pos(1129.057,917.151)}Are you Goku?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.30,0:07:57.05,Matsumoto,,0,0,10,,Are you {\c&H000000&}Son Goku?! (Sun Wukong)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.14,0:07:59.46,Staff,,0,0,10,,What do you think about that big stone?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.92,0:08:04.45,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,It was a rock. I was under the rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.57,0:08:03.37,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,{\pos(224.906,909.218)}That was Goku.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.37,0:08:04.45,Yamazaki,,0,0,0,,{\pos(190.188,905.196)}Definitely.
