Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.61,0:15:26.74,Staff,,0,0,10,,What does the song "Yume no Naka e" mean to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.18,0:15:32.61,Endo,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.81,0:15:35.56,Hamada,,0,0,0,,The interviewer is asking you a question!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.85,0:15:37.50,Yamazaki,,0,0,0,,He went into a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.85,0:15:39.46,TL Note,,0,0,0,,{\pos(704.905,66.536)}TL Note: Yume no Naka he = Into a Dream
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.49,0:15:39.77,Yamazaki,,0,0,0,,Is this some kind of hypnotism?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.78,0:15:42.74,Yamazaki,,0,0,0,,He did go into a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.88,0:15:42.97,Hamada,,0,0,0,,You're kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.85,0:15:50.96,Title 2 - White,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,100)\pos(1027.924,919.274)}Jimmy fell asleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.78,0:15:48.89,Hamada,,0,0,0,,{\pos(289.811,1035.922)}They're asking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.72,0:15:49.82,Endo,,0,0,0,,{\pos(292.83,931.341)}He's sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.09,0:15:54.74,Staff,,0,0,10,,{\fad(250,250)\pos(1033.962,1072)}Jimmy, are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.33,0:15:54.82,Jimmy,,0,0,0,,{\pos(433.207,1072)}Ah, you scared me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.10,0:15:56.73,Jimmy,,0,0,0,,Mornin'
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.74,0:16:01.21,Staff,,0,0,10,,You didn't get much sleep yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.21,0:16:03.29,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,No, I did sleep but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.37,0:16:08.77,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,I just ate so I got kinda sleepy and dozed off. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.93,0:16:13.46,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,Can I go smoke a cigarette real quick?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.68,0:16:13.41,Hamada,,0,0,0,,{\pos(185.66,901.173)}You can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.73,0:16:15.88,Staff,,0,0,10,,Please hold it in for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.96,0:16:21.26,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,{\fad(250,250)}After just 4 hours, Jimmy is assailed by {\c&H3F2DDC&}drowsiness{\c&HFFFFFF&}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.72,0:16:22.74,Title 2 - White,,0,0,0,,{\pos(724.528,692.011)}And after that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.72,0:16:30.70,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,That's too fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.93,0:16:32.04,Yamazaki,,0,0,0,,You're kidding, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.13,0:16:34.26,Endo,,0,0,0,,Jimmy, that's way too fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.02,0:16:35.92,Jimmy,,0,0,0,,It felt really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.32,0:16:26.29,Staff,,0,0,10,,What made you start smoking?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.48,0:16:34.37,Staff,,0,0,0,,{\pos(522.264,541.173)}Jimmy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.36,0:16:40.61,Staff,,0,0,10,,What made you start smoking?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.94,0:16:41.70,Yamazaki,,0,0,0,,{\pos(723.019,929.33)}It looks like you've been up for 16 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.06,0:16:43.04,Staff,,0,0,0,,{\pos(522.264,541.173)}Jimmy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.66,0:16:43.44,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.73,0:16:48.09,Staff,,0,0,10,,What made you start smoking?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.17,0:16:50.34,Staff,,0,0,0,,{\pos(605.283,589.441)}JIMMY!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.36,0:16:53.98,Staff,,0,0,10,,Wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.30,0:16:52.80,Yamazaki,,0,0,0,,{\pos(357.736,915.251)}What the hell is this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.69,0:16:54.78,Yamazaki,,0,0,0,,{\pos(357.736,915.251)}What the hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.14,0:16:56.48,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,{\pos(357.736,915.251)}This guy is a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.16,0:16:58.68,Hamada,,0,0,0,,{\pos(357.736,915.251)}This is too funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.26,0:16:58.69,Staff,,0,0,10,,Please wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.73,0:17:02.78,Staff,,0,0,10,,Jimmy... Jimmy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.94,0:17:05.24,Staff,,0,0,10,,Jimmy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.80,0:17:05.81,Hamada,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1123.019,909.217)}How many times are \Nyou gonna do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.58,0:17:07.30,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,{\pos(357.736,915.251)}I can't, I can't
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.24,0:17:07.01,Jimmy,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1135.094,690)}Ah, a cigarette.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.27,0:17:10.01,Hamada,,0,0,0,,If they showed us this during New Year's it'd be dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.06,0:17:10.10,Staff,,0,0,0,,{\pos(525.283,579.385)}Jimmy!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.66,0:17:10.10,Staff,,0,0,0,,{\pos(774.34,581.396)}Please wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.82,0:17:13.97,Staff,,0,0,10,,Alright, different question.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.05,0:17:15.20,Staff,,0,0,10,,I'll change the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.30,0:17:17.98,Staff,,0,0,10,,Okay, what did you think of middle school?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.02,0:17:22.45,Staff,,0,0,10,,What did middle school mean to you Jimmy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.18,0:17:22.38,Hamada,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1206.038,921.284)}Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.94,0:17:25.52,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,{\pos(233.962,929.33)}He's still at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.90,0:17:25.66,Hamada,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1206.038,921.284)}Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.72,0:17:30.60,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Seriously, this is against the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.78,0:17:35.54,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,The 24 hour {\c&H3F2DDC&}long interview won't be completed {\c&HFFFFFF&}if this continues.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.68,0:17:37.61,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,Therefore...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.66,0:17:38.73,Yamazaki,,0,0,0,,{\pos(342.642,877.04)}Yeah, take him somewhere cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.64,0:17:36.74,Hamada,,0,0,0,,{\pos(326.038,794.581)}They should take him outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.45,0:17:37.22,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,{\pos(316.981,724.19)}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.70,0:17:40.24,Staff,,0,0,0,,{\pos(594.717,517.039)}Jimmy!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.28,0:17:40.62,Jimmy,,0,0,0,,Can I go smoke real quick?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.64,0:17:41.72,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,{\pos(215.849,921.284)}You can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.12,0:17:45.38,Staff,,0,0,10,,We're going somewhere else to continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.62,0:17:47.96,Staff,,0,0,10,,Well then, let's go outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.54,0:17:54.80,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,Jimmy is taken out of the room in order to wake him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.97,0:17:54.24,Hamada,,0,0,0,,{\pos(211.321,913.24)}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.74,0:18:02.80,Staff,,0,0,0,,{\pos(318.491,860.95)}Do you always doze off?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.06,0:18:02.81,Jimmy,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1040,933.352)}I get sleepy after eating.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.97,0:18:06.52,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,Today is gonna be tough if you won't let me sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.61,0:18:08.97,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,!@#$%&。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.98,0:18:10.41,Staff,,0,0,10,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.37,0:18:11.66,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,{\pos(721.509,947.319)}Figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.18,0:18:13.82,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Nobody could understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.61,0:18:20.52,Staff,,0,0,10,,Jimmy, do you usually go for walks?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.78,0:18:23.28,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,Only when I need to buy something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.44,0:18:28.01,Jimmy,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,100}Surrounded by chilly air, they walk towards their {\c&H00FFEC&}destination{\c&HFFFFFF&}.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.05,0:18:30.69,Staff,,0,0,10,,Which city do you prefer, Tokyo or Osaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.73,0:18:33.37,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,There's nice things in Tokyo and nice things in Osaka so...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.37,0:18:35.94,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,I can't really pick one over the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.61,0:18:38.68,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1021.887,967.542)}It's weird how you keep slurring words.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.14,0:18:39.88,Jimmy,,0,0,0,,{\pos(316.981,856.927)}Time: 5 hours 3 minutes
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.01,0:18:40.42,Narrator,,0,0,10,,The interview will continue in this theater,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.42,0:18:42.42,Narrator,,0,0,10,,starting with the high school years.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.28,0:18:48.16,Staff,,0,0,10,,First, what sort of high school did you enter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.24,0:18:52.21,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,Well, I got into high school with a baseball recommendation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.30,0:18:54.93,Staff,,0,0,10,,How strong was your school?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.93,0:18:57.54,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,I'd say we were in the top 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.61,0:19:00.58,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,The team won a tournament with private schools...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.77,0:19:03.48,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,{\pos(771.321,1074.022)}Back then PL Gakuen High even had...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.52,0:19:06.28,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,{\pos(786.415,1072.011)}Yoshimura who later played with the Giants.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.37,0:19:08.02,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,{\pos(886.038,1072.011)}That time our school won.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.05,0:19:10.13,Jimmy,,0,0,0,,{\pos(886.038,1072.011)}It was a strong high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.93,0:19:09.56,Endo,,0,0,0,,{\pos(504.151,915.251)}That's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.16,0:19:12.29,Staff,,0,0,10,,I'm guessing practice was very intense.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.46,0:19:15.20,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,Rather than intense, I'd say it was dreadful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.30,0:19:19.65,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,Back then any mistake was quickly met with a punch.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.81,0:19:24.05,Staff,,0,0,10,,I heard that you were bullied during high school...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.13,0:19:28.66,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,Well, it was just teasing from my seniors.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.88,0:19:32.21,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,Things like making me stop a train.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.54,0:19:34.54,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,The express trains don't usually stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.57,0:19:36.50,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,and they really wanted to stop one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.54,0:19:42.98,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,So I stood naked shouting "Stop! Stop! Stop!".
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.62,0:19:44.10,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1124.528,911.229)}So they made you do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.30,0:19:46.24,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,Thankfully I did that on a straight part of the track.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.28,0:19:53.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\pos(368.302,826.76)}Spartan Days
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.60,0:19:53.00,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,Those were days of nothing but baseball, but what about his {\c&H8D42EE&}love life{\c&HFFFFFF&}?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.13,0:19:57.24,Staff,,0,0,10,,You didn't happen to get a girlfriend during high school?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.50,0:20:00.88,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,No, I wasn't really able to get a girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.09,0:20:03.60,Staff,,0,0,10,,When did you have your first kiss?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.70,0:20:07.41,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,I think it was right when I entered this world (show business)...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.41,0:20:11.86,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,with a working girl when I was 18.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.82,0:20:14.44,Endo,,0,0,0,,You keep talking about this stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.96,0:20:19.52,Staff,,0,0,10,,What did you think of high school?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.00,0:20:19.60,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,{\pos(510.189,802.514)}Eh!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.37,0:20:27.40,Jimmy,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1213.585,386.313)}The interviewer\Nstarted irritating me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.60,0:20:23.69,Staff,,0,0,10,,What are your thoughts on high school?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.18,0:20:28.69,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,Darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.81,0:20:30.69,Staff,,0,0,10,,And why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.58,0:20:36.06,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,I thought that without baseball I could have lived a happier life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.14,0:20:39.06,Title 2 - White,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,708.1)}Time: 6 hours 37 minutes
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.73,0:20:39.09,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's now around 4:40 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.60,0:20:43.33,Narrator,,0,0,10,,We change location and continue with his beginnings as performer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.56,0:20:47.41,Staff,,0,0,10,,Let's continue and talk about your apprenticeship at Yoshimoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.41,0:20:50.65,Staff,,0,0,10,,What did you do after graduating from high school?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.92,0:20:54.08,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,I graduated from high school and...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.09,0:20:57.37,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,I worked as a stagehand at the Nanba Kagetsu theater,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.42,0:20:59.92,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,closing the curtains and setting up for rakugo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.04,0:21:03.32,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,That's were I met Sanma-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.41,0:21:06.89,Staff,,0,0,10,,So you met him around that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.89,0:21:06.85,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,{\pos(721.509,937.263)}Yeah, I met him back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.10,0:21:10.73,Staff,,0,0,10,,By the way, why did you decide to join Yoshimoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.78,0:21:14.14,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,I'd say it was because since my school days Yoshimoto was...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.37,0:21:16.33,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,they've been in Osaka for a long time so...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.53,0:21:19.58,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,Yoshimoto was very entertaining,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.58,0:21:22.62,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,as an entertainer you'd want to join them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.72,0:21:24.93,Staff,,0,0,10,,{\pos(712.452,637.598)}Who joined them at the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.96,0:21:27.22,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,People like Downtown, High Heel and Tommys.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.41,0:21:31.41,Staff,,0,0,10,,So you met them all at once, at the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.58,0:21:34.78,Staff,,0,0,10,,What did you think of Downtown the first time you met them?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.80,0:21:37.97,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,I thought they were amazing. They were very funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.32,0:21:44.57,Jimmy,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\pos(300.377,679.944)}Mr. Okure
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.93,0:21:44.57,Title 2 - White,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\pos(1049.057,871.005)}Starting as a {\c&H00FFEC&}stagehand{\c&HFFFFFF&},\N Jimmy was able to begin \Nhis life as a performer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.65,0:21:49.16,Staff,,0,0,10,,Why did you decide to move on from being a stagehand?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.44,0:21:55.09,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,Sometimes I would be part of Downtown-san's performances.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.18,0:21:53.90,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1255.849,372.235)}Why are you\Nadding "-san"?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.33,0:21:57.12,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,I really liked it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.20,0:22:00.32,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,I wanted to become someone's apprentice.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.45,0:22:02.41,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,So I asked Sanma-san and he told me,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.46,0:22:05.88,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,Join someone who is kind, that way you'll be able to keep up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.98,0:22:10.93,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,Bonchi Osamu was very kind so I chose to become his apprentice.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.93,0:22:16.40,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,{\fad(250,250)}19-year-old Jimmy started his {\c&H3F2DDC&}apprenticeship {\c&HFFFFFF&}with Bonchi Osamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.57,0:22:19.52,Staff,,0,0,10,,How long were you Osamu's apprentice?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.60,0:22:21.92,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,2 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.12,0:22:26.74,Staff,,0,0,10,,Can you tell me what you liked and disliked about your teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.92,0:22:30.24,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,I disliked that he was a cheapskate.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.37,0:22:32.38,Staff,,0,0,10,,He was a cheapskate?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.33,0:22:32.36,Jimmy,,0,0,0,,{\pos(721.509,941.397)}Yeah, he was.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.48,0:22:35.60,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,If we ate something better than him he would get mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.66,0:22:38.85,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,{\pos(729.056,945.307)}One time we went to the cafeteria and he got kitsune udon while I got tempura udon.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.85,0:22:41.18,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,He shouted "Why are you eating something better!"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.21,0:22:46.09,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,I thought, "What? There's only a 50 yen difference."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.13,0:22:48.34,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,"Make sure you order the cucumber roll".
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.36,0:22:50.22,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,That was his ironclad rule at the sushi shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.06,0:22:56.72,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,{\fad(250,200}Changing the subject, we ask about the story of his {\c&H00FFEC&}first kiss{\c&HFFFFFF&}.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.84,0:23:00.82,Staff,,0,0,10,,You mentioned earlier that your first kiss was when you were 18, when you were a stagehand?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.13,0:23:01.22,Jimmy,,0,0,0,,Yes, when I was a stagehand...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.25,0:23:05.61,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,Sanma-san asked me "Are you a virgin?", I said yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.64,0:23:09.92,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,"Here, I'll give you 20000 yen, go to XXXX.", he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.00,0:23:13.17,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,"Go and then tell me how it went."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.29,0:23:17.04,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,So I went to XXXX and kissed and stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.21,0:23:20.70,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,It felt really good, so I said "I'm coming!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.76,0:23:23.53,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,and she said, "It's fine, go ahead."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.94,0:23:27.37,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,But what came out was pee so she got really mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.42,0:23:31.22,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,I told Sanma-san about my failure but he really enjoyed the story.
